ore_item_assets/steam/apps/2794030/extras/354f6faffecbe02b89c6f8f727f6346f.poster.avif?t=1710848899\" width=610 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794030/extras/354f6faffecbe02b89c6f8f727f6346f.webm?t=1710848899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794030/extras/354f6faffecbe02b89c6f8f727f6346f.mp4?t=1710848899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
